{"success": true, "message": "Fetched question.", "data": {"showTimer": true, "showAttemptInsight": true, "playSounds": true, "dontShowCorrectAnswerImmediately": false, "_id": "648b5a6f417cc3fb48d68181", "classes": [], "exams": ["615d76b2c52ffa3c944600df"], "subjects": ["615d708dbd4a37c4058ee5a8"], "chapters": ["615d6fed2b295b085ab6eba3"], "topics": [], "concepts": [], "previousYearPapers": [{"_id": "63f499861d196b49d9cd6b0e", "title": "JEE Main 2023 (29 Jan Shift 2)", "isVisible": true}], "position": 0, "type": "numerical", "level": 2, "approximateTimeRequired": 150, "question": {"text": "<p>Unpolarised light is incident on the boundary between two dielectric media, whose dielectric constants are <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>2</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>8</mn></math> (medium &ndash;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>1</mn></math>) and <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>6</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>8</mn></math> (medium &ndash; <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>2</mn></math>), respectively. To satisfy the condition, so that the reflected and refracted rays are perpendicular to each other, the angle of incidence should be&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msup><mi>tan</mi><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><msup><mfenced><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mn>10</mn><mi>&#952;</mi></mfrac></mrow></mfenced><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></msup></math>,&nbsp;the value of&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>&#952;</mi></math>&nbsp;is ______.</p><p>(Given for dielectric media, <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>&#956;</mi><mi>r</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></math>)</p>", "image": null}, "options": [], "correctValue": "7", "solution": {"text": "<p>As given in the question, we can write</p><p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>&#956;</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><msqrt><msub><mi>&#949;</mi><mi>r</mi></msub><msub><mi>&#956;</mi><mi>r</mi></msub></msqrt><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mn>2</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>8</mn><mo>&#215;</mo><mn>1</mn></msqrt><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mn>2</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>8</mn></msqrt></math>&nbsp;and</p><p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>&#956;</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><msqrt><msub><mi>&#949;</mi><mi>r</mi></msub><msub><mi>&#956;</mi><mi>r</mi></msub></msqrt><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mn>6</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>8</mn><mo>&#215;</mo><mn>1</mn></msqrt><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mn>6</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>8</mn></msqrt></math></p><p>Now applying Snell&#39;s law and considering&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>r</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>90</mn><mo>&#176;</mo><mo>-</mo><mi>i</mi></math>, we get</p><p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>&#956;</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>&#160;</mo><mi>sin</mi><mo>&#160;</mo><mi>i</mi><mo>=</mo><msub><mi>&#956;</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>&#160;</mo><mi>cos</mi><mo>&#160;</mo><mi>i</mi></math></p><p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>&#8658;</mo><mi>tan</mi><mo>&#160;</mo><mi>i</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msub><mi>&#956;</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi>&#956;</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mfrac><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mfrac><mrow><mn>6</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>8</mn></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>8</mn></mrow></mfrac></msqrt></math></p><p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>&#8658;</mo><mi>tan</mi><mo>&#160;</mo><mi>i</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mfenced><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>8</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>4</mn></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>8</mn></mrow></mfrac></mfenced><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></msup></math></p><p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>&#8658;</mo><mi>i</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>tan</mi><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><msup><mfenced><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mn>10</mn><mn>7</mn></mfrac></mrow></mfenced><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></msup></math></p><p>Therefore,&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>&#952;</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>7</mn></math>.</p>", "image": null}, "videoSolution": null, "numericalUpperLimit": 7, "numericalLowerLimit": 7, "questionLabels": [], "__v": 0, "masterId": "MOGJMPYQ60737959", "bucket": "Must Do Ques (JEE Main) - Any Difficulty", "category": null, "microConcepts": [], "imageBaseUrl": null, "helperText": null, "isRemoved": false, "cpyqbSubjects": ["61bb58181213731910ea0b70", "61c055eae8ce0dc8a5c62d33", "616057750283de43c87e3e1b", "61964fe0a5a5260118868021", "61964f81a5a526011886801d", "629f39e4ac11b26562e0625b", "616057920283de43c87e3e1e", "615f0c729476412f48314dab", "61a8a2c2e8ce0dc8a5c62d2d", "629105adee9e3ae00d63352b", "629f385f263330a77be9fa7d", "616056cd0283de43c87e3e15", "616057190283de43c87e3e18", "62962075e7f8e9ac4daeafd7", "64d50bd73df7f4a7f3017f6f", "66b79b34d4b564dfab4f94cc", "678ea9a09cc79e5f592bdc11", "67fa5fef4468eb1307ceb0ad", "6807d2ad647479b8e8696479"], "cpyqbChapters": ["61e7bd71ba5ea0509a0032eb", "61602441a74735a290c2b9d8", "6160244116d221a133c08775", "61602442734cc2aca48335d5", "61bb8210dae5f7af9600d5d0", "61964c933923ea685eb30f0b", "6160243f6067541f280c4e8f", "6160243e17040ba6b8d61b88", "61c08989c653cc4ca7b56e9e", "61964c9222879be3883b609e", "62962125b6ad3169b0d85632", "629109f2bf97d58ac676959b", "629f390f8db6a438ffb8c25b", "629f3a93a12e7977562036e0", "64eb06be3118f713ecfef05d", "66d5858ca75f05ee8564f87d", "67921d6c1d5b5072da5e9aee", "67fdff58378e1624ea7b6a74", "6809202d3a10446a207fdef7"], "cpyqbExams": ["615f0e999476412f48314daf", "616059af0283de43c87e3e23"]}}